name: Bitclout 42k
description:
This is the first edition of Bitclout 42k image. It is a large resolution image containing all the profile images of the first 42000 bitclout blockchain blocks. Each profile image is averaged out to a pixel in a reference image and rendered into this mosaic. Zoomed in, you should be able to find all profile images at 20px width each, from the first 42k blocks.
Full size image is 13900x12900 pixels.
